steps.name: Given I am login on staging env by created timestamp project
When I navigate to menu "Modules" without submenu
Then I should see Modules screen display
When I press Save button popover popup
Then I should see Header "Production" is collapsed
Then I should see Header "Staging" is collapsed
Then I should see Header "Development" is collapsed
Then I should see checkbox no Header with label "add video utils" has status unchecked
Then I should see checkbox no Header with label "add video transformation" has status unchecked
When I check checkbox on popover popup with label "add video utils"
When I check checkbox on popover popup with label "add video transformation"
When I press Save changes button popover popup
Then I should see checkbox no Header with label "add video utils" has status checked
Then I should see checkbox no Header with label "add video transformation" has status checked
When I close the popover popup
When I reset module "Cloudinary"
